哈里森离开俄亥俄州前往首都就职，但夫人安娜病重无法前往，于是他请儿子的遗孀[[简·欧文·哈里森|简·欧文·哈里森]]（{{lang|en|Jane Irwin Harrison}}）陪同前往并代理[[美国第一夫人|第一夫人]]职责，安娜计划在五月前往白宫<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.whitehouse.gov/about-the-white-house/first-ladies/anna-tuthill-symmes-harrison/ | title = Anna Tuthill Symmes Harrison | publisher = The White House | accessdate = 2020-10-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201023051936/https://www.whitehouse.gov/about-the-white-house/first-ladies/anna-tuthill-symmes-harrison/ | archivedate = 2020-10-23 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="firstladybio">{{cite web | title = First Lady Biography: Anna Harrison | url = http://www.firstladies.org/biographies/firstladies.aspx?biography=9 | publisher = The National First Ladies' Library | accessdate = 2020-10-24 | archivedate = 2018-10-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20181009221313/http://www.firstladies.org/biographies/firstladies.aspx?biography=9 }}</ref>。

抵达首都后，哈里森希望世人看到他仍然是不折不扣的蒂珀卡努英雄，而且受过良好教育，比竞选期间宣传的粗犷形象更善于思考。1841年3月4日（星期四）天气寒冷而潮湿，<ref name="Harrison's Inauguration">{{cite web | title = Harrison's Inauguration | url = https://www.loc.gov/exhibits/treasures/tr22a.html#obj14 | publisher = American Treasures of the Library of Congress | accessdate = 2020-10-24 | date = 2007-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201003005624/https://www.loc.gov/exhibits/treasures/tr22a.html#obj14 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2020-10-03 }}</ref>哈里森有意不穿大衣也不戴帽子，谢绝现成的密闭马车，顶着寒风骑马参加就职典礼，长达8445字的就职演说创下新纪录并保持至今<ref name="Harrison's Inauguration" />。虽有朋友兼辉格党同胞丹尼尔·韦伯斯特删减，但演讲仍有近两小时长。接下来他还在当晚出席全部三场就职典礼舞会<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.inaugural.senate.gov/days-events/days-event/inaugural-ball | title = Inaugural Ball | author = United States Senate | publisher = inaugural.senate.gov | date = 2013-06-10 | accessdate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304042039/https://www.inaugural.senate.gov/days-events/days-event/inaugural-ball | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，在卡鲁西沙龙举办的“蒂珀卡努”舞会约有一千人参加，每人需支付十美元（相当于2020年的299美元）门票入场<ref>{{cite web | title = Inflation Calculator | url = https://www.officialdata.org/us/inflation/1841?amount=10 | work = Inflation Calculator | publisher = Official Inflation Data, Alioth Finance | accessdate = 2020-10-24 | archive-date = 2021-01-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210103100641/https://www.officialdata.org/us/inflation/1841?amount=10 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

哈里森的就职演说详细阐述辉格党[[政纲|政纲]]，本质上是否定杰克逊和范布伦总统的政策。新总统承诺重建[[美国第二银行|美国银行]]，并根据亨利·克莱提出的[[美国体系_(经济计划)|美国体系]]（{{lang|en|American System}}）发行纸币，提升银行信贸能力。他打算在立法议程上服从国会判断，谨慎使用否决权，扭转杰克逊用行政职务充当政治回报的行径。哈里森承诺利用任命权组建合格的领导班子，而不是增强总统在政府中的地位。<ref>{{cite web | title = William Henry Harrison Inaugural Address | year = 1989 | work = Inaugural Addresses of the Presidents of the United States | publisher = Bartleby.com | url = https://www.bartleby.com/124/pres26.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200803213841/https://www.bartleby.com/124/pres26.html | accessdate = 2020-10-24 | archivedate = 2020-08-03 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = "I Do Solemnly Swear ...": Presidential Inaugurations | publisher = Library of Congress | accessdate = 2020-10-24 | archivedate = 2019-04-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190404195853/http://memory.loc.gov/cgi-bin/ampage?collId=pin_mssmisc&fileName=pin%2Fpin1402%2Fpin1402page.db&recNum=0&itemLink=r%3Fammem%2Fpin%3A%40field%28NUMBER+pin1402%29%29&linkText=0 | url = http://memory.loc.gov/cgi-bin/ampage?collId=pin_mssmisc&fileName=pin/pin1402/pin1402page.db&recNum=0&itemLink=r?ammem/pin:@field(NUMBER+pin1402))&linkText=0 }}</ref>

作为辉格党领袖，克莱还是极具影响的联邦参议员，但多次竞选总统都以失败告终。为在哈里森政府拥有举足轻重的地位，他原本严辞谴责以政府官职充当政治回报的行径，但却不能以此自我要求，在哈里森就职前及短暂的总统任期中都力图影响总统举措，甚至对内阁及其他总统任命官职人选也想越俎代庖。哈里森愤怒之下回绝参议员咄咄逼人的举动：“克莱先生，请记住我才是总统。”<ref>{{cite book | last = Borneman | first = Walter R. | title = 1812: The War That Forged a Nation | publisher = HarperCollins (Harper Perennial) | location = New York | year = 2005 | isbn = 978-0-06-053113-3 | page = 56}}</ref><ref name="Gerhardt-2013" />

除克莱以外，还有许多人想从哈里森当选获利。白宫此时还没有严格的保安措施，任何想面见总统的人都能前往，意图在新政府谋得一官半职的人蜂拥而至。哈里森的总统任期仅一个月出头，其中大部分时间就花在繁杂的社会义务以及接待来访白宫人士上。白宫行政官邸人满为患，时刻都有人等待接见。<ref name="Gerhardt-2013" /><ref name="Harrison's Inauguration" />哈里森曾在3月10日签字的信中表示：“如此众多的召唤和骚扰令我分身乏术，根本没有时间处理自己的事”<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.shapell.org/manuscript/letter-of-ill-soon-to-die-president-william-henry-harrison-suffering-harassed/ | title = Letter from Harrison to R. Buchanan, Esq. | date = 1841-03-10 | author = William Henry Harrison | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200428235027/https://www.shapell.org/manuscript/letter-of-ill-soon-to-die-president-william-henry-harrison-suffering-harassed/ | via = Shapell Manuscript Foundation | accessdate = 2020-10-24 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2020-04-28 }}</ref>。

哈里森认真履行改革行政高官任命的承诺，亲自到六个行政部门了解运作情况，还通过韦伯斯特向所有部门发出指令，任何工作人员如果拉票竞选都可能开除处理。其他辉格党人向他施压，要求任命官员时只考虑同党派人士，新总统对此抱抵制态度。3月16日，辉格党团体来到白宫要求总统解除所有民主党官员职务，对此哈里森回应：“黄天在上，我会在犯下这等罪孽前辞职！”<ref>{{cite book | last = Woollen | first = William Wesley | title = Biographical and historical sketches of early Indiana | publisher = Ayer Publishing | year = 1975 | page = 51 | isbn = 978-0-405-06896-6}}</ref>哈里森打算提名[[约翰·钱伯斯|约翰·钱伯斯]]（{{lang|en|John Chambers}}）出任爱荷华州州长时，他的内阁又企图否决总统决策，选择韦伯斯特的朋友[[詹姆斯·威尔逊二世|詹姆斯·威尔逊]]（{{lang|en|James Wilson}}）。3月25日，韦伯斯特在内阁会议上向总统施压，哈里森于是把手写的纸条递给国务卿，请他大声念出来，纸上的文字是：“威廉·亨利·哈里森，合众国总统”。总统接下来对众人言道：“威廉·亨利·哈里森，合众国总统现在告诉你们，先生们，老天作证，约翰·钱伯斯才应该当爱荷华州州长！”<ref name="Gerhardt-2013">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130131034904/http://aprg.web.unc.edu/files/2011/10/Michael-Gerhardt-APRG.pdf | url = http://aprg.web.unc.edu/files/2011/10/Michael-Gerhardt-APRG.pdf | title = The Forgotten Presidents: Their Untold Constitutional Legacy | accessdate = 2020-10-24 | author = Michael J. Gerhardt | publisher = Oxford University Press | isbn = 978-0199967797 | year = 2013 | archivedate = 2013-01-31 | deadurl = no | 11 =  }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | last = Remini | first = Robert | title = Daniel Webster: The Man and His Time | accessdate = 2020-10-24 | url = https://archive.org/details/danielwebsterman00remi | publisher = W.W. Norton & Co. | year = 1997 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/danielwebsterman00remi/page/520 520–521]}}</ref>

[[File:James_Reid_Lambdin_-_William_Henry_Harrison_-_Google_Art_Project.jpg|thumb]]

哈里森和克莱对是否有必要召集国会特别会议无法达成一致，内阁的表决结果也陷入僵局，哈里森呼吁特别会议在5月31日开始。克莱在3月13日对总统施压，哈里森拒绝妥协并且要求克莱不要再去白宫，有什么事就以书面形式告知。<ref>{{cite web | title = American History Series: The Brief Presidency of William Henry Harrison | work = Learning English | publisher = Voice of America | date = 2009-01-28 | accessdate = 2020-10-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170323021400/http://learningenglish.voanews.com/a/a-23-2009-01-28-voa3-83141382/129777.html | url = https://learningenglish.voanews.com/a/a-23-2009-01-28-voa3-83141382/129777.html | archivedate = 2017-03-23 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="Gerhardt-2013" />几天后，财政部长[[托马斯·尤因|托马斯·尤因]]告知总统，联邦政府基金所剩无几，只能等国会在12月例行开会并拨款后才能恢复运作。哈里森于是要求特别会议提前到3月17日召开，解决“国家收入和财政状况问题”。如果他没有突然去世，会议应该会在5月31日按原计划召开<ref>{{cite book | last1 = Brinkley | first1 = Alan | last2 = Dyer | first2 = Davis | year = 2004 | title = The American Presidency | publisher = Houghton Mifflin | isbn = 978-0-618-38273-6 | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=3djEYV3R7oIC&pg=PA120&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN#v=onepage&q&f=false | accessdate = 2020-10-24 | archive-date = 2021-01-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210103100700/https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=3djEYV3R7oIC&pg=PA120&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Harrison's Proclamation for Special Session of Congress | url = http://www.bobsuniverse.com/BWAH/09-Harrison/18410317a.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111004052418/http://www.bobsuniverse.com/BWAH/09-Harrison/18410317a.pdf | archivedate = 2011-10-04 | accessdate = 2011-10-04 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Proclamation 45B—Convening an Extra Session of the Congress | work = The American Presidency Project | publisher = UC Santa Barbara | accessdate = 2020-10-24 | url = https://www.presidency.ucsb.edu/documents/proclamation-45b-convening-extra-session-the-congress | archive-date = 2021-01-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210103100710/https://www.presidency.ucsb.edu/documents/proclamation-45b-convening-extra-session-the-congress | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 逝世和葬礼 ==
[[File:Death_of_Harrison,_April_4_A.D._1841.jpg|thumb]]

哈里森于1841年3月26日病倒，症状类似感冒，但此后两天逐渐恶化，医生的诊治显然没有效果<ref name="Jones31Day">{{cite journal | last = Jones | first = Marty | publisher = Historynet | accessdate = 2020-10-24 | url = https://www.historynet.com/the-thirty-one-day-presidency-of-william-henry-harrison.htm | title = The Thirty-One Day Presidency of William Henry Harrison | date = 2016-04-06 | journal = American History Magazine | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190402204742/https://www.historynet.com/the-thirty-one-day-presidency-of-william-henry-harrison.htm | archivedate = 2019-04-02 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。起初人们普遍以为他是在三周前的就职典礼上感冒致病<ref name="Cleaves-1939">{{cite book | last = Cleaves | first = Freeman | title = Old Tippecanoe: William Henry Harrison and His Time | publisher = C. Scribner's Sons | location = New York | year = 1939}}</ref>{{rp|152}}，医生诊断他患有[[肺炎|肺炎]]，具体位置是在他肺部右下叶，然后采用[[拔罐|拔罐]]、[[放血|放血]]等一系列疗法<ref name="WHHDOTP">{{Cite web | last = Freehling | first = William | title = William Henry Harrison: Death of the President | url = https://millercenter.org/president/harrison/death-of-the-president | work = Miller Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200818234023/https://millercenter.org/president/harrison/death-of-the-president | deadurl = no | publisher = University of Virginia | location = Charlottesville, Virginia | accessdate = 2020-10-24 | archivedate = 2020-08-18 | date = 2016-10-04 }}</ref>。不见好转后，医生又尝试采用[[吐根酊|吐根]]、[[蓖麻油|蓖麻油]]、[[甘汞|甘汞]]治疗，最终还将[[石油|原油]]与[[马兜铃|蛇根马兜铃]]混合后煮沸给总统服用，这些措施都导致哈里森病情恶化<ref name="Jones31Day" />。

白宫起初没有正式公布总统病情，引发外界猜测，许多人担心他会长时间离开公众视野。到了三月底，不少人在白宫外聚集并守夜，时刻等候总统情况的最新消息<ref name="Jones31Day" />。1841年4月4日，威廉·亨利·哈里森在患病九天后与世长辞，享年68岁<ref name="Cleaves-1939" />{{rp|160}}，是首位在任上去世的美国总统，而且刚刚任职一个月<ref name="WHHDOTP" />。2014年，《临床传染病》（{{lang|en|''Clinical Infectious Diseases''}}）刊登简·麦克休（{{lang|en|Jane McHugh}}）与菲利普·麦考维克（{{lang|en|Philip A. Mackowiak}}）的分析文章，两人检视米勒（{{lang|en|Miller}}）医生的笔记，并从历史纪录中得知白宫供水位于公共污水排放口下游后认为，哈里森总统很可能因“肠热”（即[[伤寒|伤寒]]或[[副傷寒|副傷寒]]）死于[[敗血性休克|败血症休克]]<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2014/04/01/science/what-really-killed-william-henry-harrison.html | title = What Really Killed William Henry Harrison? | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | first1 = Jane | last1 = McHugh | first2 = Philip A. | last2 = Mackowiak | date = 2014-03-31 | accessdate = 2020-10-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201021213450/https://www.nytimes.com/2014/04/01/science/what-really-killed-william-henry-harrison.html | archivedate = 2020-10-21 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | title = Death in the White House: President William Henry Harrison's Atypical Pneumonia | first1 = Jane | last1 = McHugh | first2 = Philip A. | last2 = Mackowiak | journal = Clinical Infectious Diseases | pmid = 24962997 | date = 2014-06-23 | doi = 10.1093/cid/ciu470 | volume = 59 | issue = 7 | pages = 990–995}}</ref>。总统临死前对主治医生说出遗言，但从内容来看应该是希望在场人士转告副总统约翰·泰勒：

{{quote|先生，我希望你了解政府的真正原则，还期盼能够落实。除此以外我别无所求。<ref>{{Cite web | title = William Henry Harrison: Key Events | url = https://millercenter.org/president/william-harrison/key-events | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200407141044/https://millercenter.org/president/william-harrison/key-events | deadurl = no | work = Miller Center | publisher = University of Virginia | location = Charlottesville, Virginia | accessdate = 2020-10-24 | date = 2016-10-07 | archivedate = 2020-04-07 }}</ref>}}

总统去世后是30天哀悼期，白宫依照欧洲皇室葬礼惯例举办各种公共仪式。4月7日，[[白宫东厢房|白宫东厢房]]举行追悼会，仅限获邀人士参加，哈里森的棺木接下来送至首都[[美国国会公墓|国会公墓]]，放在公共墓地区。<ref>{{cite web | title = William Henry Harrison Funeral: April 7, 1841 | archivedate = 2019-12-19 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191219051129/https://www.whitehousehistory.org/william-henry-harrison-funeral | url = https://www.whitehousehistory.org/william-henry-harrison-funeral | website = whitehousehistory.org | publisher = The White House Historical Association | location = Washington, D.C. | accessdate = 2020-10-24 }}</ref>据[[所羅門·諾薩普|所羅門·諾薩普]]的著作《[[被奪走的十二年|被奪走的十二年]]》记载：

{{quote|text=华盛顿第二天举办盛大活动，加农炮的轰鸣和钟声响彻云空，许多房屋笼上黑纱，街上黑压压的到处都是人。随着时间推移，游行队伍逐渐成形，缓缓穿过大街，马车辆辆紧接形成长队，成千上万的人徒步尾随，都在朝忧郁的音乐声前进。他们把哈里森的遗体抬到墓地……我依然清楚地记得，每当炮声在墓地响起，窗户的玻璃是如何破裂并掉在地面，在哗啦声中碎成千万片。<ref>{{cite web | author = Solomon Northup | url = https://docsouth.unc.edu/fpn/northup/northup.html | title = Twelve Years a Slave: Narrative of Solomon Northup, a Citizen of New-York, Kidnapped in Washington City in 1841, and Rescued in 1853 | accessdate = 2020-10-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201020220226/https://docsouth.unc.edu/fpn/northup/northup.html | via = Documenting the American South | archivedate = 2020-10-20 | deadurl = no }}</ref>}} {{Wayback|url=https://docsouth.unc.edu/fpn/northup/northup.html |date=20201020220226 }}

1841年6月，哈里森的遗体经火车和船只运到北本德，然后在7月7日下葬位于尼波山顶的家族墓地，此地能俯瞰[[俄亥俄河|俄亥俄河]]，如今已建成[[威廉·亨利·哈里森墓地州立纪念碑|威廉·亨利·哈里森墓地州立纪念碑]]<ref>{{cite web | title = William Henry Harrison Tomb | url = https://www.ohiohistory.org/visit/museum-and-site-locator/william-henry-harrison-tomb | website = ohiohistory.org | publisher = Ohio History Connection (formerly the Ohio Historical Society) | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150516080030/https://www.ohiohistory.org/visit/museum-and-site-locator/william-henry-harrison-tomb | location = Columbus Ohio | accessdate = 2020-10-25 | archivedate = 2015-05-16 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

=== 去世的影响 ===
[[File:William_Henry_Harrison_Memorial.jpg|thumb]]

《[[美国宪法|美国宪法]]》[[美国宪法第二条|第二条第一款第六段]]对[[美國總統繼任順序|总统继任程序]]的规定不够详尽。虽明确规定“总统被免职、死亡、辞职或丧失履行权力和责任能力时，总统职务应移交副总统”，但没有明确副总统只是临时承担职权，还是直接成为美国总统。<ref>{{cite journal | last = Feerick | first = John | title = The Problem of Presidential Inability--Will Congress Ever Solve It? | journal = Fordham Law Review | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160609073849/http://ir.lawnet.fordham.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1778&context=flr | url = https://ir.lawnet.fordham.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1778&context=flr | publisher = Fordham University School of Law | accessdate = 2020-10-25 | volume = 32 | issue = 1 | year = 1963 | archivedate = 2016-06-09 | deadurl = no }}</ref>

哈里森的内阁坚称泰勒是“代理总统职务的副总统”，泰勒坚决主张他直接继任总统职位并行使全部职权<ref name="ConstitutionDailyNCC">{{cite web | title = A controversial President who established presidential succession | url = https://constitutioncenter.org/blog/john-tyler-americas-most-unusual-president | date = 2017-03-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200524000221/https://constitutioncenter.org/blog/john-tyler-americas-most-unusual-president | work = Constitution Daily | publisher = National Constitution Center | location = Philadelphia, Pennsylvania | accessdate = 2020-10-25 | archivedate = 2020-05-24 | deadurl = no | author = NCC Staff }}</ref>。咨询[[美国首席大法官|首席大法官]][[罗杰·B·托尼|罗杰·B·托尼]]后，内阁要求泰勒按总统规格宣誓后继任，泰勒同意并于1841年4月6日宣誓就职。五月国会开幕后，两院经过短暂辩论发布决议，确认泰勒继任总统并完成哈里森剩下的任期。<ref>{{cite journal | last = Rankin | first = Robert S. | title = Presidential Succession in the United States | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-politics_1946-02_8_1/page/44 | journal = The Journal of Politics | date = 1946-02 | volume = 8 | issue = 1 | jstor = 2125607 | pages = 44–56 | doi = 10.2307/2125607}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1111/j.1741-5705.2005.00269.x | last = Abbott | first = Philip | title = Accidental Presidents: Death, Assassination, Resignation, and Democratic Succession | journal = Presidential Studies Quarterly | date = 2005-12 | volume = 35 | issue = 4 | pages = 627–645 | jstor = 27552721}}</ref>泰勒创下的先例于1967年通过[[美利坚合众国宪法第二十五条修正案|第25条修正案]]写入宪法，至今已沿用七次，而且都是在任总统死亡后副总统继任<ref name="ConstitutionDailyNCC" />。

辉格党人本希望通过税收并制定各种措施支持克莱的美国体系，但哈里森的死令他们期望落空。泰勒上任后抛弃党派章程并被开除出党。<ref>{{cite web | title = John Tyler, Tenth Vice President (1841) | publisher = United States Senate | url = https://www.senate.gov/artandhistory/history/common/generic/VP_John_Tyler.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190507034234/http://www.senate.gov/artandhistory/history/common/generic/VP_John_Tyler.htm | accessdate = 2019-05-07 | archivedate = 2019-05-07 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>1841年共有三人先后担任美国总统：范布伦、哈里森和泰勒，这种情况之后只在1881年出现过，三位总统分别是[[拉瑟福德·伯查德·海斯|拉瑟福德·伯查德·海斯]]、[[詹姆斯·艾布拉姆·加菲尔德|詹姆斯·艾布拉姆·加菲尔德]]和[[切斯特·艾伦·阿瑟|切斯特·艾伦·阿瑟]]<ref name="americanhistory.about.com">{{cite web | last = Kelly | title = Did Tecumseh’s Curse Kill Seven US Presidents? | publisher = ThoughtCo | url = https://www.thoughtco.com/tecumsehs-curse-and-the-us-presidents-105440 | accessdate = 2020-10-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200914214014/https://www.thoughtco.com/tecumsehs-curse-and-the-us-presidents-105440 | archivedate = 2020-09-14 | deadurl = no | first = Martin }}</ref>。

== 影响 ==
[[file:William_Henry_Harrison._Indiana_statehood_stamp,_1950_issue.jpg|thumb]]

=== 历史评价 ===
[[File:Tecumseh_in_Lafayette_IN.jpg|thumb]]的蒂珀卡努县法院大楼上有哈里森塑像（左）]]

纵观哈里森一生事迹，担任印第安纳领地总督期间与印第安人谈判或签署的各项条约对后世影响最为深远<ref name="Gugin-St. Clair-2006" />{{rp|18}}。各印第安部落通过谈判割让西部大片土地，为移民买地定居提供更广阔的空间<ref name="cb" /><ref name="Madison-Sandweiss-2014" />{{rp|47}}<ref name="Barnhart-Riker-1971" />{{rp|409–410}}。

哈里森的竞选方法为现代总统竞选策略奠定基础<ref name="Green-2007" />{{rp|100}}，他也是首位在职期间拍下照片的总统，是就职典礼当天在华盛顿哥伦比亚特区拍摄。如今虽有约翰·昆西·亚当斯、安德鲁·杰克逊和马丁·范布伦的照片存世，但都是在他们卸任总统过后很久所拍。哈里森在就职典礼日拍下的[[银版摄影法|银版照片]]已经遗失在历史长河，但至少[[大都會藝術博物館|大都會藝術博物館]]还有一张早期照片存档。<ref>{{cite web | title = The Met Collection Database | publisher = [[大都會藝術博物館|Metropolitan Museum of Art]] | archivedate = 2019-05-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190509235821/https://www.metmuseum.org/art/collection/search/190020170 | url = https://www.metmuseum.org/art/collection/search/190020170 | accessdate = 2020-10-25 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = The Oldest Known Photographs of a U.S. President | date = 2013-02-05 | author = Megan Garber | url = https://www.theatlantic.com/technology/archive/2013/02/the-oldest-known-photographs-of-a-us-president/272872/ | archivedate = 2020-09-30 | deadurl = no | newspaper = The Atlantic | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200930205220/https://www.theatlantic.com/technology/archive/2013/02/the-oldest-known-photographs-of-a-us-president/272872/ | accessdate = 2020-10-25 }}</ref>

哈里森去世时几乎不名一文，国会经表决赠予他的遗孀安娜2.5万美元养老金<ref name="Damon 1974-06">{{cite journal | last = Damon | first = Allan L. | title = Presidential Expenses | journal = American Heritage | date = 1974-06 | volume = 25 | issue = 4 | url = https://www.americanheritage.com/presidential-expenses#6 | accessdate = 2020-10-25 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2020-08-29 | quote = William Henry Harrison was virtually penniless... beginning with a $25,000 payment to Mrs. Harrison in 1841 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200829183851/https://www.americanheritage.com/presidential-expenses#6 }}</ref>，相当于哈里森一年的薪酬（相当于{{inflation-year|US}}的{{formatnum:{{Inflation|US|25000|1841|r=-3}}}}美元）<ref>{{cite web | author = Federal Reserve Bank of Minneapolis | url = https://www.minneapolisfed.org/about-us/monetary-policy/inflation-calculator/consumer-price-index-1800- | title = Consumer Price Index, 1800– | access-date = 2020-10-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201019024223/https://www.minneapolisfed.org/about-us/monetary-policy/inflation-calculator/consumer-price-index-1800- | archive-date = 2020-10-19 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。此外，她还获许今后寄信免除邮费<ref name="firstladybio" />。

哈里森之子约翰·斯科特是1853至1857年间的俄亥俄州联邦众议员<ref name="bioguide.congress">{{cite dictionary | title = Harrison, John Scott, (1804–1878) | dictionary = Biographical Directory of the United States Congress | url = https://bioguideretro.congress.gov/Home/MemberDetails?memIndex=H000272 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20181003013853/http://bioguide.congress.gov/scripts/biodisplay.pl?index=H000272 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2018-10-03 | accessdate = 2020-10-25 }}</ref>。哈里森之孙本杰明曾于1889至1893年当选第23任美国总统，至今两人仍是史上仅有的爷孙总统<ref>{{cite book | last = Calhoun | first = Charles William | title = Benjamin Harrison: The 23rd President 1889–1893 | series = The American Presidents | volume = 23 | publisher = Macmillan | location = New York | year = 2005 | isbn = 978-0-8050-6952-5 | pages = 43–49}}</ref>。

=== 纪念 ===
2009年2月19日，[[美國鑄幣局|美國鑄幣局]]发行[[总统1美元硬币计划|总统1美元硬币计划]]第九弹，上刻哈里森肖像，共出产9842万枚<ref>{{Cite web | title = William Henry Harrison Presidential $1 Coin | publisher = [[美国铸币局|United States Mint]] | url = https://www.usmint.gov/coins/coin-medal-programs/presidential-dollar-coin/william-henry-harrison | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201017081752/https://www.usmint.gov/coins/coin-medal-programs/presidential-dollar-coin/william-henry-harrison | archive-date = 2020-10-17 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2020-10-25 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.usmint.gov/about/production-sales-figures/circulating-coins-production?program=Presidential+One+Dollar&+50StateQuartersyears=&+WestwardJourneyNickelSeries%E2%84%A2years=&+PresidentialOneDollaryears=753&+DistrictofColumbiaandUSTerritoriesQuartersyears=&+AmericatheBeautifulQuarters%C2%AEyears=&+CirculatingCoinsyears= | title = Circulating Coins Production Figures: usmint.gov | publisher = United States Mint | access-date = 2020-10-25 | archive-date = 2021-01-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210103100840/https://www.usmint.gov/about/production-sales-figures/circulating-coins-production?program=Presidential+One+Dollar&+50StateQuartersyears=&+WestwardJourneyNickelSeries%E2%84%A2years=&+PresidentialOneDollaryears=753&+DistrictofColumbiaandUSTerritoriesQuartersyears=&+AmericatheBeautifulQuarters%C2%AEyears=&+CirculatingCoinsyears= | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

美国多地建有纪念物向哈里森致敬，[[印第安納波利斯|印第安納波利斯]]市中心<ref name="Greiff-2005">{{cite book | last = Greiff | first = Glory-June | title = Remembrance, Faith and Fancy: Outdoor Public Sculpture in Indiana | publisher = Indiana Historical Society Press | year = 2005 | location = Indianapolis | isbn = 0-87195-180-0}}</ref>{{rp|12, 164}}，[[辛辛那提|辛辛那提]]的[[皮亚特公园|皮亚特公园]]（{{lang|en|Piatt Park}}）<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.waymarking.com/waymarks/WM42AG_Statue_of_William_Henry_Harrison_Cincinnati_Ohio | publisher = Groundspeak | title = Statue of William Henry Harrison - Cincinnati, Ohio - American Guide Series on Waymarking.com | website = www.waymarking.com | access-date = 2020-10-25 | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308080118/https://www.waymarking.com/waymarks/WM42AG_Statue_of_William_Henry_Harrison_Cincinnati_Ohio | dead-url = no }}</ref>、印第安纳州[[拉法葉_(印第安纳州)|拉法叶]]的[[蒂珀卡努县法院|蒂珀卡努县法院]]<ref name="Greiff-2005" />{{rp|243}}、[[哈里森縣_(印地安納州)|哈里森县]]<ref name="Greiff-2005" />{{rp|131}}、[[歐文縣_(印地安納州)|欧文县]]都有他的塑像公开展示<ref name="Greiff-2005" />{{rp|206}}。印第安纳州、[[哈里森縣_(愛阿華州)|爱荷华州]]、[[哈里森縣_(密西西比州)|密西西比州]]和[[哈里森縣_(俄亥俄州)|俄亥俄州]]都有以他姓氏命名的县<ref>{{cite book | url = https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_9V1IAAAAMAAJ | title = The Origin of Certain Place Names in the United States | publisher = Govt. Print. Off. | last = Gannett | first = Henry | year = 1905 | page = [https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_9V1IAAAAMAAJ/page/n149 150] | accessdate = 2020-10-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite book | last = Funk | first = Arville | title = A Sketchbook of Indiana History | year = 1969 | edition = Revised 1983 | publisher = Christian Book Press | location = Rochester, Indiana | page = 118}}</ref>，此外还有多地以他的姓氏或“蒂珀卡努”命名<ref>{{Cite book | title = Ohio town names | last = Overman | first = William Daniel | publisher = Akron, Ohio | hdl = 2027/mdp.39015015361465}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.visittippcity.org/history-photos/ | title = History & Photos | website = VisitTippCity.org | access-date = 2016-10-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161011035556/http://www.visittippcity.org/history-photos/ | archive-date = 2016-10-11 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。至少有三所高中以他命名，其中两所位于印第安纳州<ref>{{cite web | title = Welcome to Harrison High School! | publisher = Intrado | work = Harrison High School | url = https://harrison.evscschools.com/about_us | archivedate = 2020-07-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200721175334/https://harrison.evscschools.com/about_us | accessdate = 2020-10-25 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Welcome to William Henry Harrison High School | publisher = Tippecanoe School Corporation | url = https://hhs.tsc.k12.in.us/about-us/welcome | accessdate = 2020-10-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200920000257/https://hhs.tsc.k12.in.us/about-us/welcome | archivedate = 2020-09-20 }}</ref>，一所在俄亥俄州<ref>{{cite web | title = School Profile | publisher = William Henry Harrison High School | url = https://www.southwestschools.org/william-henry-harrison-high-school/about-our-school-17/school-profile-17/ | accessdate = 2020-10-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20060722224243/http://www.southwestschools.org/hsindex.html | archivedate = 2006-07-22 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

时至今日，俄亥俄州北本德依然会在每年2月9日哈里森生日前后举办巡遊活动向他致敬<ref>{{cite news | title = In Greater Cincinnati, one of America's most obscure presidents gets a parade | newspaper = Cincinnati Enquirer | author1 = Carl Weiser | author2 = Jeff Suess | author3 = Sharon Coolidge | accessdate = 2020-10-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200217192903/https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/us/in-greater-cincinnati-one-of-americas-most-obscure-presidents-gets-a-parade/ar-BB104ft8%3Focid%3Dspartanntp | archivedate = 2020-02-17 | url = https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/us/in-greater-cincinnati-one-of-americas-most-obscure-presidents-gets-a-parade/ar-BB104ft8 | deadurl = no | date = 2020-02-17 }}</ref>。俄亥俄州[[哥伦布_(俄亥俄州)|哥伦布]]的[[富兰克林顿_(俄亥俄州哥伦布)|富兰克林顿]]（{{lang|0en|Franklinton}}）至今保有威廉·亨利·哈里森将军总部，是1813至1814年间哈里森的军事总部，俄亥俄州如今只剩这幢建筑与他有关<ref name="nrhpdoc">{{cite web | url = https://catalog.archives.gov/id/71988611 | title = National Register of Historic Places Registration Form | publisher = [[美国国家公园管理局|National Park Service]] | accessdate = 2020-10-25 | archive-date = 2021-02-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210225030545/https://catalog.archives.gov/id/71988611 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

